<p>(责编：张雪冬、刘泽) </p>
➜贫困村换新貌 百姓乐开颜
http://www.sohu.com/a/433885650_114731	7341
<p align="center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201124/8c7bb1fd612047bc8b894e56e4d211ba.jpeg" /></p>
<p align="center">航拍镜头下的壕口村。</p>
<p align="center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201124/fa2f63e5aec34e728a64b6cad4f57515.jpeg" /></p>
<p align="center">散养的农家鸡。</p>
<p align="center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201124/f3e74dade5814a9e96a468528db9a26b.jpeg" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
